snippet.title: STARBO - Official Game Trailer
snippet.description:
The official STARBO game trailer.

When a plane crashes in the Caribbean Sea, a passenger ends up in a mysterious adventure far beyond the set reality he once knew.

Get STARBO today on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/774321/STARBO
